      "instruction": "1. Bring a large pot of water to a boil. Cook the noodles according to package directions. Drain.2. Add the noodles to a large bowl and add the shrimp, carrots, radishes, bell peppers, and cucumbers. Add 1/2 the sauce and toss to combine. Divide among bowls and top with avocado, basil, and cilantro. Sprinkle with peanuts. Serve with remaining sauce.&nbsp;"
